    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Assoċjazzjoni tal-Istati tal-Karibew"@mt, "Kariibi Riikide Liit"@et, "Comhlachas Stáit Mhuir Chairib"@ga, "Associazione degli Stati dei Caraibi"@it, "Karību jūras reģiona valstu apvienība"@lv, "Združenie karibských štátov"@sk, "Karibian valtioiden liitto"@fi, "Association of Caribbean States"@en, "Asociația Statelor din Caraibe"@ro, "Stowarzyszenie Państw Karaibskich"@pl, "Asociación de Estados del Caribe"@es, "Sammanslutningen av västindiska stater"@sv, "Associatie van Caribische Staten"@nl, "Assoziation karibischer Staaten"@de, "Асоциация на карибските държави"@bg, "Karibų jūros valstybių asociacija"@lt, "Karibi Államok Társulása"@hu, "Association des États des Caraïbes"@fr, "Associação dos Estados das Caraíbas"@pt, "Asociace karibských států"@cs, "Sammenslutningen af Caribiske Stater"@da, "Ένωση των κρατών της Καραϊβικής"@el, "Združenje karibskih držav"@sl, "Udruženje karipskih država"@hr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Association of Caribbean States is a union of nations centered on the Caribbean Basin. It was formed with the aim of promoting consultation, cooperation, and concerted action among all the countries of the Caribbean."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "ACS"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "ACS"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001040"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
