    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Spoločné parlamentné zhromaždenie AKT–EÚ"@sk, "Paritätische Parlamentarische Versammlung AKP–EU"@de, "Paritaire Parlementaire Vergadering ACS–EU"@nl, "ĀKK un ES Kopējā parlamentārā asambleja"@lv, "ACP–EU Joint Parliamentary Assembly"@en, "AVS–EU:s gemensamma parlamentarisk församling"@sv, "Den Paritetiske Forsamling AVS–EU"@da, "AKV–ELi parlamentaarne ühisassamblee"@et, "Adunarea parlamentară mixtă ACP–UE"@ro, "Assemblea parlamentare paritaria ACP–UE"@it, "Zajednička parlamentarna skupština AKP–EU"@hr, "L-Assemblea Parlamentari Konġunta AKP–UE"@mt, "Asamblea Parlamentaria Paritaria ACP–UE"@es, "AKCS–EU Közös Parlamenti Közgyűlés"@hu, "Assemblée parlementaire paritaire ACP–UE"@fr, "Společné parlamentní shromáždění AKT–EU"@cs, "Skupna parlamentarna skupščina AKP–EU"@sl, "Μεικτή Κοινοβουλευτική Συνέλευση ΑΚΕ–ΕΕ"@el, "Wspólne Zgromadzenie Parlamentarne AKP–UE"@pl, "Comhthionól Parlaiminteach ACC–AE"@ga, "AKT:n ja EU:n yhteinen parlamentaarinen edustajakokous"@fi, "Assembleia Parlamentar Paritária ACP–UE"@pt, "Съвместна парламентарна асамблея на АКТ–ЕU"@bg, "AKR ir ES jungtinė parlamentinė asamblėja"@lt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "ACP-EU_JPA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "ACP-EU_JPA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0000362"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/ACP-EU_JPA_2009_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "ACP-EU_JPA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "ACP-EU_JPA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "ACP-EU_JPA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "2009-12-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "ACP-EU_JPA";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#historyNote> "The ACP–EU Joint Parliamentary Assembly was created to bring together the elected representatives of the European Union the Members of the European Parliament and the elected representatives of the African, Caribbean and Pacific states \"ACP countries\" that have signed the Cotonou Agreement. Since the entry into force of the Treaty on European Union and EU enlargement it has acquired a more prominent role. A substantial part of the work of the JPA is directed towards promoting human rights and democracy and the common values of humanity, and this has produced joint commitments undertaken within the framework of the UN conferences."@en
}
