    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Kolombo planas"@lt, "Colomboplanen"@da, "Colomboplanen"@sv, "Colombo plaan"@et, "План „Коломбо“"@bg, "Piano di Colombo"@it, "Načrt iz Kolomba"@sl, "Tíortha Phlean Colombo"@ga, "Plan de Colombo"@es, "Plan de Colombo"@fr, "Plan iz Colomba"@hr, "Plano de Colombo"@pt, "Colombo Plan"@en, "Colombo-Plan"@de, "Planul Colombo"@ro, "Kolombo plāns"@lv, "Colombo-suunnitelma"@fi, "Σχέδιο του Κολόμπο"@el, "Plán z Kolomba"@sk, "Kolombský plán"@cs, "Plan z Colombo"@pl, "Colombo-terv"@hu, "Pjan ta’ Kolombo"@mt, "Colombo-plan"@nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Colombo Plan is a regional organisation that embodies the concept of collective intergovernmental effort to strengthen economic and social development of member countries in the Asia-Pacific region. The primary focus of all Colombo Plan activities is on human resources development."@en;
