<..\\..\\..\\index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4a1a399ec7ecda12a9eebc4460b240dd>.
<#4a1a399ec7ecda12a9eebc4460b240dd> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/ETUI>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T00:53:35.694Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#4a1a399ec7ecda12a9eebc4460b240dd> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/ETUI> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#exactMatch> <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/1449>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Европски синдикални институт"@sr, "Istitut Ewropew tat-Trade Unions"@mt, "Euroopa Ametiühingute Instituut"@et, "Euroopan ammattiyhdistysinstituutti"@fi, "Europejski Instytut Związków Zawodowych"@pl, "Europees Vakbondsinstituut"@nl, "Evropski sindikalni inštitut"@sl, "European Trade Union Institute"@en, "Istituto sindacale europeo"@it, "Instituto Sindical Europeu"@pt, "Institutul Sindical European"@ro, "Europeiska fackföreningsinstitutet"@sv, "Institut syndical européen"@fr, "Evropský odborový institut"@cs, "Európai Szakszervezeti Intézet"@hu, "Ευρωπαϊκό Συνδικαλιστικό Ινστιτούτο"@el, "Europski sindikalni institut"@hr, "Europos profesinių sąjungų institutas"@lt, "Det Europæiske Fagforeningsinstitut"@da, "Instituto Sindical Europeo"@es, "Eiropas Arodbiedrību institūts"@lv, "Европейски синдикален институт"@bg, "Europäisches Gewerkschaftsinstitut"@de, "Európsky odborový inštitút"@sk, "Institiúid Eorpach na gCeardchumann"@ga;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "L’Institut syndical européen est le centre indépendant de recherche et de formation de la Confédération européenne des syndicats, qui regroupe elle-même les organisations syndicales d’Europe. L’ETUI met ses compétences – acquises notamment dans le cadre de ses réseaux académiques, universitaires et d’experts – au service de la défense des intérêts des travailleurs au niveau européen et au renforcement du volet social de l’Union européenne. L’Institut est composé de deux départements : Un département Recherche avec trois unités : Européanisation des relations industrielles; Politiques économiques, sociales et de l’emploi; Conditions de travail, santé et sécurité; Un département de Formation."@fr, "The European Trade Union Institute (ETUI) is the independent research and training centre of the European Trade Union Confederation which itself affiliates European trade unions into a single European umbrella organisation. The ETUI places its expertise – acquired in particular in the context of its links with universities, academic and expert networks – in the service of workers’ interests at European level and of the strengthening of the social dimension of the European Union. The Institute is composed of two departments: a research department with three units: Europeanisation of industrial relations; Economic, employment and social policies; Working conditions, health and safety; an education department."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "ETUI"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "ETUI"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001287"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "ETUI"@en, "ETUI"@hr, "EVI"@nl, "EPSI"@lt, "ETUI"@pl, "EAI"@lv, "DEFI"@da, "EGI"@de, "ISE"@es, "ISE"@fr, "ISE"@it, "ISE"@pt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/ETUI_2005_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "ETUI";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "ETUI";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "ETUI";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "2005-04-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "ETUI"
}
<..\\..\\..\\index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#aee60c85e50929876d274390867b741d>.
<#aee60c85e50929876d274390867b741d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EUTELSAT>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T00:53:35.710Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#aee60c85e50929876d274390867b741d> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EUTELSAT> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#exactMatch> <http://eurovoc.europa.eu/6160>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "An tAontas Eorpach Báirse"@ga, "Eutelsat"@sl, "Eutelsat"@fr, "Eutelsat"@da, "Eutelsat"@tr, "Eutelsat"@nl, "Eutelsat"@pl, "Eutelsat"@pt, "Eutelsat"@sv, "Eutelsat"@it, "Eutelsat"@ro, "Eutelsat"@hu, "Eutelsat"@en, "Eutelsat"@sk, "Eutelsat"@lv, "Eutelsat"@mt, "Eutelsat"@de, "Eutelsat"@es, "Евтелсат"@bg, "EUTELSAT"@lt, "EUTELSAT"@fi, "EUTELSAT"@el, "EUTELSAT"@et, "EUTELSAT"@hr, "EUTELSAT"@sr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The organisation first took shape in order to operate the first generation of communications satellites ordered by the European Space Agency. Geopolitical changes after the fall of the Berlin Wall transformed Eutelsat’s original scope to serve customers in Western Europe. The organisation’s membership progressively expanded from the early 1990s to include all Eastern European countries. In step with the liberalisation of the telecoms sector, Eutelsat’s assets and activities were transferred from the intergovernmental organisation into a private company in July 2001."@en, "L’organisation a pris forme afin d’exploiter la première génération de satellites de communication commandés par l’Agence spatiale européenne. Après la chute du Mur de Berlin, l’évolution du cadre géopolitique a modifié la vocation originale d’Eutelsat qui était de desservir l’Europe de l’Ouest. L’organisation s’est progressivement ouverte à tous les pays d’Europe orientale à partir du début des années 90. Avec la libéralisation du secteur des télécommunications, les actifs et les activités d’Eutelsat ont été transférés de l’organisation intergouvernementale à une société de droit privé en juillet 2001."@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "COB0001286"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "EUTELSAT"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "EUTELSAT"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "Euroopa Satelliitside Organisatsioon"@et, "Europäische Fernmeldesatellitenorganisation"@de, "Organisation européenne des télécommunications par satellites"@fr, "Den Europæiske Telekommunikationssatellitorganisation"@da, "Eiropas Satelītsakaru organizācija"@lv, "Euroopan tietoliikennesatelliittijärjestö"@fi, "Organizzazzjoni Ewropea tat-Telekomunikazzjonijiet bis-Satellita"@mt, "Europejska Organizacja Łączności Satelitarnej"@pl, "Organização Europeia de Telecomunicações por Satélite"@pt, "Evropská telekomunikační satelitní organizace"@cs, "Европейска организация за спътникови съобщения"@bg, "Organizația Europeană de Telecomunicații prin Satelit"@ro, "Európai Műholdas Távközlési Szervezet"@hu, "Európska organizácia telekomunikačných satelitov"@sk, "Organización europea de telecomunicaciones por satélite"@es, "Europese Organisatie voor telecommunicatiesatellieten"@nl, "Evropska organizacija za satelitske telekomunikacije"@sl, "Europska organizacija za telekomunikacije putem satelita"@hr, "European Telecommunications Satellite Organization"@en, "Europeiska telesatellitorganisationen"@sv, "Europos telekomunikacinių palydovų organizacija"@lt, "Organizzazione europea delle telecomunicazioni via satellite"@it, "Ευρωπαϊκός Οργανισμός Δορυφορικών Επικοινωνιών"@el;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EUTELSAT_1977_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "EUTELSAT";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "EUTELSAT";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "EUTELSAT";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1977-01-01";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "EUTELSAT"
}
